Palindrome inside the palindrome: degeneracy structure, SWAP proof, optical cavity

Discovery and proof session (April 3, 2026):

PROVEN (Tier 1):
- d_real(1) = 2N for ANY connected graph (SWAP invariance + triangle inequality)
