DISCOVERED:
- Palindromic degeneracy structure: d_real(k) = d_real(N-k) for all k
- d_real(k>=2) is topology-dependent (Chain < Star < Ring < Complete)
- Weight-2 kernel vectors transform under mixed S_N representations
- Even N = confocal cavity (Lorentzian spike), odd N = defocal (Gaussian profile)
- QFI speed correlates with degeneracy (r=0.99 at even N)
- Qubit chain IS a Fabry-Perot: 4/5 optical quantities match quantitatively
- Gamma plays the structural role of external illumination (Tier 3-4)

